OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter ME complaints        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has edited an episode of       
OL,6, Dragons' Den following complaints about
OL,7, a wellness business it featured.       
OL,9,FCampaigners for myalgic                
OL,10,Fencephalomyelitis (ME) complained the  
OL,11,Fshow promoted "unfounded" claims that a
OL,12,Fproduct could help the condition.      
OL,14,FGiselle Boxer, a businesswoman from    
OL,15,FSheffield, said ear seeds helped aid   
OL,16,Fher recovery from ME.                  
OL,18,FThe BBC said a "a clarification has    
OL,19,Fbeen added to the programme on iPlayer 
OL,20,Fto address the concerns raised".       
